description:
Dino Academy is in session! Dino Academy Preschool Games is a fun, colorful, free to download, educational app for toddlers, preschoolers, and kindergartners ages 1 through 6! Encourage a love of lifelong learning with over 1000 educational activities and games for important school subjects like Math, English, and so much more! Learning basics like ABCs, counting, and colors has never been this fun before!

In our interactive Dino Academy, we let kids get the opportunity to explore and learn about the world around them. From toddlers to kindergartners, every child can have the opportunity to learn important subjects while having fun. Our vast library of activities is specially designed to engage and develop your child’s creativity while they learn!

With the help of our Common Core-aligned programs, you can boost your child’s confidence in future educational success. Engage your child with stimulating and fun activities that let their imaginations run free and strengthen their blossoming mind! 

Dino is waiting to learn and play! Download Dino Academy Preschool Games to start your child’s path to a love of lifelong learning!

Key Features:

Fun Games & Activities
- Play colorful Math games for counting, addition, and subtraction practice
- Practice English for any skill level: from ABCs to basic reading!
- Our Library of educational games and activities offer endless fun and learning
- Play fun games like Whack a Bunny, Match, Memory, and so much more!
- Paint with creative options to let your child express themselves

Kids Learn More, You Worry Less
- With over a thousand educational activities, parents can keep their children engaged
- All of our activities and stories combine fun and learning
- Intuitive mechanisms make it easy for toddlers to navigate through the app 
- Kids can explore our app without their parent’s supervision
- Without ads or links to social media, your kids can learn and explore without distractions
- Intuitive mechanisms make it easy for toddlers to navigate through the app 

Learn More with Dino Academy
- Our cute Dino Avatar guides and encourages your child through fun activities!
- Excite your child with painting activities to boost creativity
- Solve fun and colorful puzzles meant to support basic logical reasoning
- Kids can make their way through vivid and interactive mazes
- Let your kids listen to our wholesome and fun stories to spark their imagination

Information for Parents
- Dino Academy Preschool Games is perfect for children between the ages 1 and 6

- Subscribe to receive the entire Tiltan Games educational library for kids

Subscription Information:
- Cancel your subscription at any time
- Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current pay period
- Payment is charged to your iTunes Account once you confirm your purchase.
- Account is charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current billing period
- Manage your subscriptions from your account on the App Store
- Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when you purchase a subscription.

Schools and Kindergarten Program: For Teachers and School Representatives
Contact us at info@tiltangames.com to find out more about our School Program.

Join the fun today with Dino Academy Preschool Games!

Tiltan Games Team
